orthyiam.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Worthy Iam</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>h0x0r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(5/15/01 3:08:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Some questions on Death Pact.</span><hr size=1> Just a few questions on this spell please.<br>
<br>
1) I heard it's success was based on Charisma. Any truth to that? (I usually get a buff to get my Charisma up to 125 prior to casting. I am not a pretty Cleric.)<br>
<br>
2) I heard it only has a 25% chance of working, no matter what. Any verification on that?<br>
<br>
3) How much is healed? (I have used it, and had it go off durring raids, but, in the chaos, I never really got a good answer.)<br>
<br>
Any information is appriciated. Thanks! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
